xyz.kotlout.kotlout.model.experiment

Class Experiment

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.kotlout.kotlout.model.experiment.Experiment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BinomialExperiment, CountExperiment, MeasurementExperiment, NonNegativeExperiment

    public abstract class Experiment
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Base class for modelling experiments. Child classes should model a particular type of experiment. Which likely contain a list of a type of trial.
    See Also:
